entry.title: Ukraine Races to Restore Electricity, Water Supplies After Russian Strikes
entry.content: Utility crews across Ukraine were working to restore water and electricity supplies after a barrage of Russian missiles a day earlier knocked out service to hundreds of thousands of people.
